OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1778000754
OL,3,CMan arrested after suspected arson at
OL,4,Cdisused Co-op building
OL,6,FA man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof arson following a large fire at an
OL,8,Fabandoned building in County Durham.
OL,10,FEmergency services were were alerted
OL,11,Fto the incident on Woods Terrace, in
OL,12,FMurton, on Thursday 30 April at around
OL,13,F6:19pm.
OL,15,FFirefighters spent several hours
OL,16,Ftackling the fire at the former Co-op
OL,17,Fbuilding.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/4
