OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1778000754
OL,3,CMan arrested after suspected arson at
OL,4,Cdisused Co-op building
OL,6,FA spoksperson from County Durham and
OL,7,FDarlington Fire and Rescue Service
OL,8,F(CDDFRS) said: "A total of four fire
OL,9,Fengines and an aerial ladder platform
OL,10,Fwere in attendance.
OL,12,F"Firefighters wearing breathing
OL,13,Fapparatus spent several hours tackling
OL,14,Fthe fire before leaving the scene."
OL,16,FDurham Constabulary said they arrived
OL,17,Fat the scene "at around 6:25pm."
