OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1778000754
OL,3,CMan arrested after suspected arson at
OL,4,Cdisused Co-op building
OL,6,FA spokesperson from the force said:
OL,7,F"Crews from County Durham and
OL,8,FDarlington Fire and Rescue Service
OL,9,Falso attended and brought the fire,
OL,10,Fwhich is being treated as arson, under
OL,11,Fcontrol.
OL,13,F"A 33-year-old man was arrested on
OL,14,Fsuspicion of arson and brought into
OL,15,Fpolice custody, where he remains today
OL,16,F(1 May)."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/4
